data.description: Enjoy country living in this 2+ bedroom rancher! Home sits on almost 5 acres of land with a huge pond, outbuildings and a barn. It wont take much to provide the finishing touches on the basement space...loads of potential! The walkout basement also provides a workshop that opens up to the 20 x 40 outbuilding and 20 x 30 barn. The gas cooktop is run by a small propane tank. The rest of the house is electric.
